author: @ilayzairem9830
text:
In this song, jennie's rap at the beginning is the same with The Notorious Big's kick in the door song in some parts and its rhythm is the same. Lisa's song part is the same with some lyrics and rhythm of Rihanna's pon de replay song. and the last sentence is from 50 cent's P.I.M.P song. maybe you can override my last statement because the words might be the same by chance. But we've been waiting for a comeback for 2 years and Yg has been pretty lazy about their comeback ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ. Anyway, it's not the girls' fault, as far as I know.

but yang hyung-suk please give these girls an original, bombshell comeback please *ORIGINAL*. I think the song is beautiful, especially jenlisa rap  and jisoo's parts are also important, and jisoo is not taken into the background, which made me very happy. Rose's electric guitar part... was so perfect. When I say rose, I think of soft girl but she brought out her bad girl personality in this song. But it would be much nicer if it was completely original. I say this for girls because
many antis are talking about it now and some blinks are now anti rather than blink. this makes me sad. please yg should pay more attention to comebacks. by the way, isn't it time for jisoo's solo to come? I think jisoo should release at least 2 songs and jennie should release 1 more in the future. but let's prioritize jisoo how many years have we been waiting for jisoo's solo... and gone isn't getting enough attention!! Why?! Lisa was also discriminated against at the awards ceremony... you deserve the best, girls. Keep it up. we also want a series like blackpink house to come again as tr-blinks. I love you girls...❤️‍🔥🇹🇷🤍💘💐 this that pink venom…

author: @RLWillow
text:
As an American it was nice to see how much we love BP. YOU Ladies deserve it and so much more. Jisoo, Jennie, Rosé and Lisa, Thank you so much for staying true to yourselves and never giving up. And thank you for staying humble and doing everything with grace. These past few weeks I have watched just abt everything BP and it's just amazing. Everything from the pink house to the diaries to every music video and it all just amazes me what you have accomplished. So let's give them a hand Blinks and applaud them! Thank each one of you!
Thank you Lisa for that bright smile that you use to pick everyone when one of you is sad.
Jennie, Thank you for having a beautiful heart and the way you make others feel around you. 
Rosé, Thank you for being pure of heart and always wanting to try new things even when you get scared. 
Jisoo, Thank you for looking out for your girls and making sure they know they are loved. In my opinion you and Jennie are like the parents pretty much lol. So thank you both for always keeping each other safe. Awesome job Ladies and we can't wait for more Wonderful music and videos. 🖤B4L💖 IYA!
